      m_Calls: []
  m_text: Welcome to the Unit Management and Team Editor Menu. You can customise
    the attacks of your units and chage your team layout here. The Numbers 1, 2 and
    3 represent a team slot respectively with contain up to 4 units each. There are
    4 prefab units which you can add to the roster in the new units tab. The existing
    units tab consists of units which were used in levels or saved by you manually.
    The attacks tab can only be accessed when a unit is selected. Click on one of
    the units to start. If a unit reaches level 2, it can evolve into a new class
    and an evolve button will appear. You can choose 2 paths.
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 9e0efe2e5a895214389f76165a6b16c7, type: 2}
